01:20:25,071 --> 01:20:26,573
তোমার হাত দেখি।

1217
01:20:28,366 --> 01:20:30,410
বেশ।

1218
01:20:30,494 --> 01:20:32,996
<font color="#ff80ff"><i>♪ Trapeze ♪</i></font>

1219
01:20:33,079 --> 01:20:36,208
<font color="#ff80ff"><i>♪ You played a two-faced game
